[img]http://i51.tinypic.com/348ipeb.jpg[/img][b] ZodiacsReign is a tool pack and newly reformed utility to make your private server coding much more easier and much more faster, ZodiacsReign tools have been around for 2 years in the RSPS community. In most ZodiacsReign series items you will find ID list, tools and other essentials for proficient RSPS coding.[/b]
[size=12pt][font=andale mono][b]What's New?[/font][/size][b] ZodiacsReign is now taking a new step toward the next generation of tools and ID list. My good friend Red Bar Pk has completely converted the V.11 Pack into a utility so you guys could access things much more faster, it will have the same content but will have a brand new concept that I hope you guys enjoy.[/b] [img]http://i52.tinypic.com/312v8sm.jpg[/img] [URL=http://www.mediafire.com/zodiacsreign][IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/dfeukl.jpg[/img][/URL]
[img]http://i56.tinypic.com/i50nc8.jpg[/img] [img]http://i53.tinypic.com/22kw06.jpg[/img] [img]http://i41.tinypic.com/20jfdhs.jpg[/img]
[size=23pt]Main Credits[/size] Z 0 D I A C/ZodiacsReign Red Bar Pk And Previous Credits.
[center][size=18pt]Quotes[/size] [b]Lin Moparscape Veteran[/b] : Nice job. Why don't you work on a server though? The packages out there aren't going to get any better than this to be honest.
[b]Galkon[/b] : Great job, I'll definitely use tools in this.
[b] Hidendra, Mopar Vet[/b] : DON'T WORRY THERE'S NO VIRUSES EVERYONE, SO DON'T ASK FOR TWO FUCKING VIRUS SCANS or i will kill you
[b]Cocoa, Blaze-Scape Creator[/b] : I already have this one on my computer, This is the best pack yet imo.
[center][i]ZodiacsReign 11.0 Utility was made by Z 0 D I A C of Moparscape/R-S Forums and Red Bar Pk of Emps-Scape & Released on October 24,2010
